<emphasis bold="true" box="[786,798,1278,1299]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">7</emphasis>
. Male holotype, carapace and tergites (5), coxosternal area and sternites III–V (7). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[388,487,1302,1323]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Figures 6</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[541,553,1302,1323]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">8</emphasis>
. Female paratype from the type locality, carapace and tergites (6), coxosternal area and sternites III–IV (8).
</paragraph>
